","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0269"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-08-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:02.477","remediation":"立即升级到 Netscape Enterprise Server 4.1 及以上版本，该版本已修复 PageServices 目录列表漏洞。如无法升级，在服务器配置中禁用 PageServices 功能或删除相关 CGI 脚本。鉴于 Netscape Enterprise Server 已停止维护，建议迁移至 Apache HTTP Server 或 Nginx 等现代 Web 服务器。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0269","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/22611","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/1999/CVE-1999-0269.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0269.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0269","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0269.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0269.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-qqpc-2hm2-rq5r/GHSA-qqpc-2hm2-rq5r.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/netscape_PageServices.nasl","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0269.json","https://github.com/idabeygunarathna/network-scanning-kali/blob/a0d5890e2fe9f211390468c6077814becf5610d6/nikto_report.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0455.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0454","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0454.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0268","title":"MetaInfo MetaWeb 文件上传与脚本执行漏洞","description":"MetaInfo MetaWeb Web 服务器存在未授权脚本上传与执行漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过 HTTP 请求向目标服务器上传任意脚本文件，并直接访问执行该脚本，从而获取服务器控制权或执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 MetaWeb 多个版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。目前厂商已停止维护，建议用户迁移至其他 Web 服务器软件。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0268"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:02.347","remediation":"立即停止使用 MetaInfo MetaWeb 服务器，该产品已停止维护且无安全更新可用。迁移至受支持的 Web 服务器（如 Apache HTTP Server 或 Nginx），并配置严格的上传权限控制，禁止脚本文件在可写目录下执行。如无法立即迁移，应将服务器置于隔离网络并限制外部访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/110","http://www.osvdb.org/3969","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19084","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/1999/CVE-1999-0268.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0268.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0268","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0268.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0268.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-pmvg-g2g6-mpp9/GHSA-pmvg-g2g6-mpp9.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0268.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82098/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0454.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0453","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0453.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0752","title":"Netscape Enterprise Server SSL Handshake 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Netscape Enterprise Server 的 SSL 握手处理过程中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向目标服务器发送特制的 SSL 握手请求触发该溢出，导致服务进程崩溃从而引发拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Netscape Enterprise Server 3.6 及更早版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0752"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-06T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:58.993","remediation":"建议将 Netscape Enterprise Server 升级至 4.0 或更高版本以修复 SSL 握手缓冲区溢出漏洞。由于该产品已停止维护，长期方案应迁移至仍在支持的 Web 服务器（如 Apache HTTP Server 或 Nginx）。临时缓解措施可在网络层限制异常 SSL 握手请求频率。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0752","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19416"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0453.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0452","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0452.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0267","title":"NCSA HTTPd 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"NCSA HTTPd 1.3 版本存在远程缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送特制的 HTTP 请求触发该漏洞，导致缓冲区越界写入，进而实现远程命令执行。该漏洞影响 NCSA HTTPd 1.x 系列版本，无需身份认证即可远程利用，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0267"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-09-23T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:02.227","remediation":"NCSA HTTPd 已停止维护多年，建议立即迁移至 Apache HTTP Server 2.4.x 或 Nginx 等现代 Web 服务器。迁移后需重新配置虚拟主机、访问控制和 SSL 证书，并关闭旧服务器上的 80/443 端口。如无法立即迁移，可在防火墙层面限制对 80 端口的访问来源 IP 作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/