ed":"1998-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:02.100","remediation":"立即从 Web 服务器移除 info2www CGI 脚本目录（通常位于 /cgi-bin/info2www），或删除 info2www 文件。如仍需此类功能，改用维护中的替代方案（如 Pinfo）。通过 Web 服务器配置限制 CGI 目录执行权限，确保仅授权用户可执行，并在 WAF 层过滤包含特殊字符（如 |、;、`、$()）的 CGI 请求参数。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1995","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20430","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/1999/CVE-1999-0266.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0cda26301f5b3e56ace35e3d98835812d878db41/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0266.json","https://github.com/geeknik/the-nuclei-templates/blob/36a6d14bce3293907a83afb498caec5fd45b1777/CVE-1999-0266.yaml","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0266","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-1999-0266.yaml","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0266.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0266.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5j6c-65fm-f6cr/GHSA-5j6c-65fm-f6cr.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/web-cgi.rules"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0451.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0449","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0449.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0265","title":"Novell NetWare 3.12 ICMP Redirect Message 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Novell NetWare 3.12 操作系统在处理 ICMP 重定向消息时存在输入验证不当漏洞（CWE-20）。远程攻击者可向目标主机发送特制的 ICMP 重定向数据包，触发系统处理异常，导致目标系统崩溃或挂起，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞无需身份认证即可利用，攻击复杂度低，影响 Novell NetWare 3.12 版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0265"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:01.977","remediation":"建议升级至 Novell Open Enterprise Server (OES) 当前维护版本以获得完整安全支持。如暂无法升级，可在 NetWare 服务器上通过设置 SET ALLOW ICMP REDIRECT = OFF 禁用 ICMP 重定向处理；同时在网络边界防火墙配置规则，丢弃入站的 ICMP 类型 5（重定向）报文，以阻断远程攻击路径。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ154174","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0265.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0265.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0265","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0265.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0265.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/icmp.rules","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0265.md","https://github.com/bailehang/snort_2.2.0/blob/34f8a3a85f15645aea53d6e0d46863c7c57e43ef/doc/signatures/473.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0265.json","https://github.com/slacker247/GPDA/blob/fa9006d0877a691f1ddffe88799c844a3e8a669a/Sodi/Run/IDSrules/rule.386"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0449.toml"}]